<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
  <head>
    <meta content='text/html; charset=UTF-8' http-equiv='Content-Type' />
  </head>
  <body>
    <h1>Your item <%= @item.name %> was not approved.</h1>
    <p>
      The reason that this item was denied access onto
      the site was either because the item image itself was
      empty, or the item was found to be inappropriate.
    </p>
    <p>
      If you can revise the item that was just sent
      then maybe it will be able to be approved the next
      time around. Its no big deal and the review team
      would be happy to point you into the right direction
      for your item to be processed.
    </p>
    <p>
      To edit this item just follow this link: <%= @url %>.
      Once there just click the edit button to edit your
      item.
    </p>
    <p>Your friends the Review Team</p>
  </body>
</html>
